We enable all of your human capital to join together to create solutions that truly make giant leaps forward—things that change business so much that you could never go back to the old way.

sub_fields.label: Staff Slider
sub_fields.name: staff_slider
sub_fields.instructions:
Add one slide per staff member.

All images must be of the same width and height in order for slider to work properly (eg. 491px by 738px).

sub_fields.label: Icon
sub_fields.name: icon
sub_fields.instructions: Copy and paste the svg code for the desired icon. SVG code is necessary in order to achieve rollover states
